@startuml YashwantChauhan_SDL

actor User
participant "Web Browser" as Browser
participant "Django Views" as Views
participant "Django Models" as Models
database "SQLite Database" as DB
participant "ML Classifier" as ML

User -> Browser: Access IDS website
Browser -> Views: GET request

alt User not authenticated
    Views -> Browser: Show login/signup page
    User -> Browser: Enter credentials
    Browser -> Views: POST credentials
    Views -> Models: Validate user
    Models -> DB: Query user data
    DB --> Models: Return user data
    Models --> Views: User validated
    Views -> Browser: Redirect to dashboard
else User authenticated
    Views -> Browser: Show dashboard
end

User -> Browser: Upload traffic file
Browser -> Views: POST file
Views -> Models: Process file
Models -> ML: Classify traffic
ML --> Models: Return classification
Models -> DB: Save results
DB --> Models: Confirm save
Models --> Views: Return results
Views -> Browser: Display results and recommendations

User -> Browser: View history
Browser -> Views: GET history
Views -> Models: Fetch history
Models -> DB: Query history data
DB --> Models: Return history data
Models --> Views: Return history
Views -> Browser: Display history

@enduml